---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure | HtownGuide"
  description="HtownGuide affiliate disclosure: how we earn revenue, which programs we participate in, and our commitment to honest recommendations."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pt-20 pb-24">
    <span class="block text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-[color:var(--color-clay)] mb-4">Disclosure</span>
    <h1 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-5xl tracking-tight leading-tight mb-10 text-balance">
      How HtownGuide makes money.
    </h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--color-ink-soft)] text-pretty">
      <p>
        HtownGuide participates in affiliate marketing programs. When you click a link to a hotel, tour, or other service on our site and make a booking or purchase, we may earn a small commission at no additional cost to you.
      </p>
      <p>
        Programs we may participate in include (but are not limited to): Booking.com, GetYourGuide, Viator, Amazon Associates, and OpenTable.
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl tracking-tight pt-6 text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">
        Editorial independence
      </h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate revenue does not influence our recommendations. We do not accept payment in exchange for coverage, and we do not write reviews on assignment from the businesses we cover. Every recommendation on this site is a place we'd genuinely send a friend.
      </p>
      <p>
        If a business stops being worth recommending, we'll change the listing or remove it — regardless of whether they pay a commission.
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl tracking-tight pt-6 text-[color:var(--color-ink)]">
        FTC disclosure
      </h2>
      <p>
        In accordance with FTC guidelines (16 CFR Part 255), we disclose that some links on this site are affiliate links. Specifically, links labeled "Book on Booking.com," "Reserve via OpenTable," "Tour on GetYourGuide," or similar may pay us a commission if you complete a transaction.
      </p>
      <p>
        Questions about this disclosure? <a href="/contact" class="text-[color:var(--color-clay)] underline decoration-1 underline-offset-4">Get in touch</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
